---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Inspect account activity

Usage: activity <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list      List recent activity
  info      Show information about one activity record
  like      Like one activity record
  unlike    Unlike one activity record
  comments  Add or remove activity comments
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
